'''''Perrero v. Disney and HCL''''' was a lawsuit filed in the [[United States]] state of [[Florida]] by Leo Perrero, a former Disney World employee, against Disney World and HCL for using [[H-1B visa|H-1B]] workers to displace American workers including Perrero from their jobs. A similar case was filed by Dena Moore against Disney and Cognizant. The case was decided against the plaintiffs.

